Header Two: Using commas or tabs inside a csv file...
To learn how to import a CSV into Markdown...
It's quite complicated but easily copy-pasteable.
Folder containing CSV files MUST be named _data.
Nothing else will be read. Not even _Data or _files.
You can type certain markdown in a CSV file...
...and it will render correctly, which is kind of insane.
Not all markdown is currently supported.
It's recommended to use few columns and more rows...
